Implementation Plan
Phase 1: Project Restructuring (Week 1)
Create monorepo structure with pnpm/npm workspaces
Move backend to /apps/api with Vercel serverless adapter
Move frontend-admin to /apps/admin with updated configuration
Create shared package for TypeScript types
Phase 2: Backend Adaptation for Serverless (Week 2)
Install @vercel/serverless-adapter and configure NestJS
Remove WebSocket dependencies and implement alternative real-time solution
Update Prisma configuration for serverless connection pooling
Convert file uploads to use Vercel Blob or external storage
Phase 3: Frontend Integration (Week 3)
Update API client configuration to use relative paths (/api/v1)
Configure Next.js middleware for authentication
Implement Server-Sent Events (SSE) for real-time updates
Update environment variables for Vercel deployment
Phase 4: Vercel Configuration & Deployment (Week 4)
Create vercel.json with proper routing rules
Set up build commands for both apps
Configure environment variables in Vercel dashboard
Set up external PostgreSQL (Vercel Postgres, Supabase, or AWS RDS)
Deploy and test staging environment
Key Technical Decisions
1. WebSocket Alternative: Server-Sent Events (SSE)
Problem: Vercel serverless functions don't support persistent WebSocket connections
Solution: Replace Socket.io with SSE for real-time notifications
Implementation: Create /api/v1/events endpoint for event streaming
Fallback: Use polling for critical real-time features
2. Database Strategy
External PostgreSQL: Use Vercel Postgres, Supabase, or AWS RDS
Connection Pooling: Configure Prisma with connection_limit for serverless
Migrations: Run Prisma migrations during build phase
3. Authentication Flow
JWT Tokens: Continue using current JWT implementation
Cookie-based auth: Consider for better serverless compatibility
Middleware: Implement Next.js middleware for route protection
4. File Storage
Vercel Blob: For uploaded files and assets
External CDN: For static assets and media
Vercel Configuration (vercel.json)
{
  "buildCommand": "pnpm build",
  "devCommand": "pnpm dev",
  "installCommand": "pnpm install",
  "outputDirectory": ".next",
  "framework": "nextjs",
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/api/:path*", "destination": "/apps/api/:path*" },
    { "source": "/admin/:path*", "destination": "/apps/admin/:path*" },
    { "source": "/(.*)", "destination": "/apps/admin/$1" }
  ],
  "functions": {
    "apps/api/**/*.ts": {
      "maxDuration": 30
    }
  }
}

